            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7718A.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to St G. J. Mivart, 21 April [1870]</ref>, and <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7170.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from St G. J. Mivart, 22 April 1870</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD refers to Mivart 1865, 1866a, 1866b, and 1867.</note>
